name: kandranghzxu - Kinectic under-Root (system)
description:
The kndrncgzxu system is said to be one of the main nourishers of the under levels of the planetary layer. As a unstoppable force, it blooms its fillament roots across all extension
of the primary contact with the minrals. Once obtained its core parasytical relation to the transmutation process, it waves its elemental births in and out of dimensions, making and disconnecting the prana energy in a molecular deep extend. It's longes roots, reach as far down as the core can get, and pierce de inner system like the rhizomes of time-space. This, is where they are born.
